Later, the LaBelle family asked for an apology in writing, but received no response.
LaBelle’s lawyer and representative did not respond to calls asking for an opinion.
The lawsuit is for an unspecified compensation, but the family's lawyer, Sam Davis, said he doesn't charge a fee and the family is planning to donate the money they get to child cancer care.
