The city tender on the 16 gates reopens the debate on the importance of Collserola in Barcelona.
In the mid-1980s, at the height of the now-disappeared Corporaci<0xC3><0xB3>n Metropolitana de Barcelona (CMB), this administration published its libel on the promotion of Collserola.
