The question arises of itself: Collserola, park or mountain?
Not only from an organisational point of view, but also with a view to reflecting on the city is the topic of discussion at the mouth of all architects from Barcelona.
It’s almost a recurring theme that two members of this old caste who meet in the elevator can resort to.
