Miguel Rold<0xC3><0xA1>n, Daniel Modol and Marta Bayona: The tender is appropriate.
For Rold<0xC3><0xA1>n "it is necessary" to talk about the "front at the mountains" after the attack on the coast, insofar as the discourse of Ildefons Cerda, who over the green apples, has not been carried out.
