We must embark on a new stage of European development.
In order to create the republic in France, it was necessary to “create” Republicans.
The revolution of interests alone could not do enough here.
This instruction remains valid.
We need to form a better integrated Europe at an economic level.
This can only be achieved by creating a more politically democratic Europe, a truly European People's Sovereignty.
